<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l4">Reyn vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒogen</expan> in Peyern etc . des <expan>heılıge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Römıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l5">Reıchs <expan>kurfürſte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
