<ab>Den <expan>hochwirdig<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>hochgeborn<ex>en</ex></expan> fursten und
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> czu Meincz, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        Otten czu Tryer, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Dietreiche<ex>n</ex></expan> zu Cölln,
                            <expan>erczbischoffe<ex>n</ex></expan>, und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Ludweig<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>pfallnczgraf<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        bey Reyn und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czogen</expan> in peyern etc.,<lb/> des
                                <expan>heilige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> reichs <expan>kurfürste<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Hochwirdig<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>hochgeborn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>furste<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>und<ex>er</ex>tenig</expan> willig dienst sein
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiss
                        voran bereyt. <expan>Gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, wie sich ewr
                                <expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade zu
                                <expan>Beparte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>und<ex>er</ex>redt</expan> und <expan>beslosse<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        habt, auf den tag zu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, den der
                                <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> durchlewchtigist fürst und
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Sigmund
                                <expan>römisch<ex>er</ex></expan> zu <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
